    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is paired with a desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox, sending power through a variable M-differential lock. Technical highlights include a double-VANOS system that pulls cleanly through the rev range and a chassis that has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical upgrade for structural integrity. The suspension maintains its factory-spec damping characteristics, providing the precise turn-in and communicative feedback expected from the M-division. While the finish shows minor road-going patina consistent with a well-loved performance machine, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this a turn-key specimen for the canyon carver or track-day enthusiast.",
