      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it's honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for getting around town and the occasional road trip. It runs like a dream and the interior is still looking great! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it drives. It's the perfect balance of quality and value\u2014ready to hit the road with a new owner today!",
