      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque to the rear wheels via a variable M-differential lock. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and a refreshed suspension setup featuring Bilstein dampers. Recent technical maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and a precision valve clearance adjustment to ensure optimal timing and compression. The braking system utilizes cross-drilled rotors with high-friction pads for consistent thermal management. This is a driver-centric machine with a documented service history, ready for the apex.",
